column2: SELECT ra,dec FROM DR1#.galaxyData OPEN my_cursor -- WHILE(#=#) BEGIN   FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into @ra, @dec   IF (@@fetch_status < #) break   INSERT MYDB.MyTable_#   SELECT * FROM dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(@ra,@dec,#) END -------------------- -- close the cursor -------------------- CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
